#SLSChampionshipTour

Catch @margielyndidal in Salt Lake City August 27-28th for Stop 1 of the 2021 Championship Tour!

VIP tickets available now on Streetleague.com, link in bio ⛓

📱- @antclaravall @tyrone.romero

2013 👉2017. Excited to see what @nyjah brings to the 2021 Championship Tour, kicking off in 16 days in Salt Lake City! 👀

#SLSChampionshipTour
